high_descs: Turn to your right then move few steps, turn right then head to the counter top on you right
Pick up the egg on the counter top
Turn right walk straight then head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in the egg wait for it then pick it up and close the fridge
Turn to your right  walk few steps then face the microwave on your left
Open the microwave and put in the egg

high_descs: Turn right and go as far as the door on the left then turn right, go as far as the fridge then turn right and go to the counter and turn right
Pick up the egg from the counter
Turn right and go to the fridge
Put the egg in the fridge and wait a bit then take the egg out of the fridge
Turn right and go to the microwave that is next to the fridge
Put the egg in the microwave

high_descs: Turn around and go right and then right again and then turn right towards the counter with the salt shaker on it.
Pick the egg up from the counter.
Go to the right and face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the egg in and shut the door and then open the door and pick the egg up again and shut the fridge door.
Move to the right to face the microwave.
Put the egg in the microwave and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled egg in the microwave.
